{{marine-geo-stub}}

{{Cleanup|reason=The correction needed to mention the exact date / month and year when DST was discontinued originally.|date=March 2017}}

Mauritius's DST period started on the last Sunday in October, and ended on the last Sunday in March.

It was re-introduced in 2008<ref>http://www.timeanddate.com/news/time/mauritius-daylight-saving-time.html</ref>
[[Mauritius]] did not repeat DST since 2009.

